opam-version: "2.0"
version: "9.2.0"
synopsis: "Compatibility package name for Rocq 9.2 core"
description: """
Compatibility package for libraries whose opam metadata or findlib metadata
still names coq-core.  Rocq 9.2 supplies the implementation through rocq-core
and rocq-runtime; this package exposes legacy findlib aliases for the engine
and Ltac plugin surfaces required by the pinned ecosystem packages.
"""
